
- Use the MeteorJS stack to create a blogging app that is available to view before signing in.

- Each user will have their own blog. Each blog entry will consist of: Title, Description, Date/Time, User. 

- Each user can have CUD functionality after signing in.

To Install this demo,
1 - Install meteor https://www.meteor.com/install 
    curl https://install.meteor.com/ | sh
    
2 - Download latest code from github (git clone https://github.com/padmashrimallapur/blog.git) 

3 - Change directory to blog directoy 
    - cd blog/blog 
    - meteor ---> this will start app on localhost (http://localhost:3000) by default port will be 3000, you can change port
    with --port option (meteor --port <port number>
